648
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:26,860
<i>Apa jenisnya?</i>

649
00:35:26,860 --> 00:35:28,070
<i>Kau mencuri kertas ujian.</i>

650
00:35:28,070 --> 00:35:31,070
